---
// src/components/Hero.astro
const waUrl = "https://wa.me/tu_numero";
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: murl('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iNDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDAiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PGc fillPSJub25lIiBmaWxsLXJ1bGU9ImV2ZW5vZGQiPjxwYXRoIGQ9Ik0wIDBoNDB2NDBIMHoiLz48cGF0aCBkPSJNMzkgMGgx djQwSDM5eiBNMCAzOWg0MHYxSDB6IiBmaWxsPSIjMDAwIi8+PC9nPjwvc3ZnPg==');"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 border border-amber-200">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500"></span>
          </span>
          Disponibilidad Inmediata
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-[100px] font-black leading-[0.85] text-zinc-900 tracking-tighter">
          MUROS QUE <br/> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-400 to-zinc-900">INSPIRAN.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="mt-8 text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed border-l-8 border-amber-500 pl-6">
          Elevamos la construcción en seco al nivel de alta costura. Precisión en cada placa, arte en cada acabado.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href={waUrl} class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-zinc-900 text-white font-bold rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">
            <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
                INICIAR PROYECTO 
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                </svg>
            </span>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-amber-500 translate-y-[100%] group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
          </a>
          <button class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-zinc-200 text-zinc-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors">
            VER PORTAFOLIO
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl border-[12px] border-white rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154526-990dced4db0d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Drywall luxury finish" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-zinc-900 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl text-white -rotate-3 hidden md:block">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black">NIVEL 5</p>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Calidad de Acabado</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>